That's what you say
about everything.

1252
01:05:21,797 --> 01:05:24,864
You don't get excited.
Why? 'cause you don't
do nothing.

1253
01:05:24,933 --> 01:05:28,000
You don't cook like me,
you don't act like
the show folks,

1254
01:05:28,068 --> 01:05:30,968
you don't work
on the towboat.
What do you do?

1255
01:05:31,036 --> 01:05:32,936
Well, i just
shelled them peas.

1256
01:05:33,004 --> 01:05:34,336
You ain't
picking them up.

1257
01:05:34,405 --> 01:05:36,971
No. I could have
if you didn't do it.

1258
01:05:37,040 --> 01:05:38,873
I could do
a lot of things

1259
01:05:38,941 --> 01:05:40,374
