¶ when it's rainin',
who's the fella ¶

1281
01:06:48,051 --> 01:06:50,117
¶ uses up
the whole umbrella? ¶

1282
01:06:50,185 --> 01:06:52,519
¶ selfish
as a man can be ¶

1283
01:06:53,720 --> 01:06:55,988
¶ no matter
what you say ¶

1284
