¶ you don't make money ¶

1286
01:07:03,759 --> 01:07:05,160
¶ i know that, honey ¶

1287
01:07:05,227 --> 01:07:07,227
¶ i never seen none ¶

1288
01:07:07,295 --> 01:07:09,495
¶ ain't going to
be none ¶

1289
01:07:09,563 --> 01:07:12,164
¶ but that don't
worry me none ¶

1290
01:07:12,231 --> 01:07:13,732
¶ no, sirree ¶

1291
01:07:13,799 --> 01:07:16,099
shiftless, lifeless,
no good!

1292
