¶ "does you do them?
No, you don't" ¶

1303
01:07:56,591 --> 01:07:59,560
¶ "will you do them?
No, you won't" ¶

1304
01:07:59,627 --> 01:08:01,327
¶ always imitatin' me ¶

1305
01:08:01,395 --> 01:08:03,395
¶ and always
aggravatin' me ¶

1306
01:08:03,463 --> 01:08:05,162
¶ then, in spite of
everything ¶

1307
01:08:05,231 --> 01:08:07,264
¶ in spite of
all the grief
you bring ¶

